window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Gigi thought she'd never fall in love, but then he rode into her world covered in ink and wrapped in chaos. </p> <p>Pike never expected his past to follow him into his future, but nothing stays hidden for long. </p> <p><i>Burn </i>is book two in the Men of Inked: Heatwave series by <i>Wall Street Journal </i>and <i>USA Today </i>best-selling author Chelle Bliss. The Men of Inked: Heatwave series features steamy romance, hot heroes, and strong women.</p>"; 
